sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri ?string
WHERE {
       res:Millipede dbp:classis ?string .
       ?uri rdfs:label ?string .
}

languageToQuestion.en: Which classis does the Millepede belong to?

sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri ?string 
WHERE {
        res:Bill_Clinton dbo:child ?child .
        ?child dbp:spouse ?string .
        ?uri rdfs:label ?string .
}

languageToQuestion.en: Who is the daughter of Bill Clinton married to?
